  1. Transformer ce graphique en diagramme sectoriel 
  data_cam<-ResMetBE17%>%
    group_by(`LibellÃ© de famille de mÃ©tier`)%>%
    summarise(met=sum(met))%>%
    ungroup()%>%
    mutate(pct = prop.table(met) * 100,
           somcum=cumsum(pct),
           rsomcum=rev(cumsum(rev(pct))),
           milieu=rsomcum-pct/2,
           labels=paste0(round(pct,1), '%'))
  
g3<- data_cam%>% 
  ggplot(aes(x='', y = pct,fill=`LibellÃ© de famille de mÃ©tier`)) + 
  geom_bar(stat = 'identity',width = 1)+
  coord_polar(theta = "y",start = 0)+
  geom_text(aes(x=1.2, y=milieu,label=labels),
          color="#FFFFFF",
          fontface="bold",
          size=3.3
          )+
  theme(
    axis.text.x=element_blank(),
    axis.title.x = element_blank(),
    axis.title.y = element_blank(),

Data_Met_Int<-
  ResMetBE17%>%
  select(`code mÃ©tier BMO`,`nom_metier BMO`,REG,NOM_REG,met)%>%
  filter(`code mÃ©tier BMO` %in% c("M2Z90","N0Z90"))%>%
  group_by(`code mÃ©tier BMO`,`nom_metier BMO`,REG,NOM_REG)%>%
  summarise_at(vars(met),funs(sum))%>%
  ungroup()%>%
  group_by(`code mÃ©tier BMO`,`nom_metier BMO`)%>%
  mutate(pct = prop.table(met) * 100)


g5<- Data_Met_Int%>%

Data_Met_Int_Carto<-
  ResMetBE17%>%
  filter(`code mÃ©tier BMO` %in% c("M2Z90","N0Z90"))%>%
  select(REG,NOM_REG,met)%>%
